we said when we delete a file on our work directory
it will remain on stage area
so we should use
"git add file_name"
to remove it from stage area to!

Note: we can see all files on current stage are by
      "git ls-files"
      it will show all files on stage.


Note: so we need two step to remove a file (removing + updating stage)
      git has a command to make it one step,
      instead remove file by OS,
      remove it by git
      in this situation git will remove it both
      from work directory & stage!

      git rm file_Name (remove that file)

      git rm .     (remove all files!)

      git rm txt.  (remove text files)

